A former client of Artie's
shot at us.

31:04.920 --> 31:06.456
Cops have an APB out.

31:06.460 --> 31:08.109
Cool. Is that cool?

31:08.120 --> 31:09.667
I don't know.
Uh, yeah, maybe.

